OL,6,FA manager of a GP surgery in Port
OL,7,FTalbot who stole more than #320,000
OL,8,Ffrom the business has been jailed.
OL,10,FAs practice manager at Fairfield
OL,11,Fsurgery Clare Boland, 51, paid herself
OL,12,Fthousands of pounds a month on top of
OL,13,Fher #53,000 salary, disguising the
OL,14,Ffraud as payments to a locum doctor.
