OL,6,F"At the time of the fraud the
OL,7,Fdefendant was practice manager, a role
OL,8,Fwhich meant she had sole
OL,9,Fresponsibility for the surgery's
OL,10,Ffinances including organising payment
OL,11,Fto doctors and staff and paying bills
OL,12,Fand expenses."JThe court heard how the
OL,13,Ffraud was uncovered in February 2022
OL,14,Fwhen a doctor at the surgery noticed a
OL,15,Fpayment of #9,000 had been paid to a
OL,16,Flocum doctor who had only worked once
OL,17,Fa week at the surgery some years
OL,18,Fpreviously.
