OL,6,FWhen the payroll company was alerted,
OL,7,Fit emerged that regular payments in
OL,8,Fthe sums of thousands of pounds had
OL,9,Fbeen made to that same account since
OL,10,FAugust 2017.
OL,12,FThe bank account belonged to Boland
OL,13,Fand it was uncovered that a total of
OL,14,F#324,706.85 had been paid into it
OL,15,Fbetween August 2017 and February 2022.
