OL,6,FThe prosecutor added that when
OL,7,Fpartners at the surgery spoke her
OL,8,Fabout the payments, Boland told them
OL,9,Fit was an administrative error and the
OL,10,Fpayments should have been recorded as
OL,11,Fgoing to HMRC instead.
OL,13,FThe court heard she was suspended from
OL,14,Fwork in March 2022 and invited to a
OL,15,Fnumber of meetings to discuss the
OL,16,Fsituation but declined to attend
OL,17,Fsaying she was unwell. She was later
OL,18,Farrested at her home.
