OL,6,FThe prosecutor said the theft of the
OL,7,Fmoney has put the surgery at
OL,8,F"substantial financial risk", left
OL,9,Fstaff "devastated" and had a
OL,10,F"significant emotional impact" on the
OL,11,Ftwo partners in the practice.
OL,13,FSentencing her to three years, Judge
OL,14,FCatherine Richard said she had taken
OL,15,Finto account Boland's guilty plea and
OL,16,Fthe "significant impact" it would have
OL,17,Fon her child.
